Central Bank Should Manage Interest Rate Margins, Financial News Reports

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-02-27T23:22:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-27/central-bank-should-manage-interest-rate-margins-financial-news-reports.html
The People’s Bank of  China  should
manage interest rate margins instead of setting the lending and
deposit rates directly, according to a report written by a
research team at the central bank’s Xi’an branch published in
the Financial News newspaper today,  The Financial News newspaper is published by the People’s
Bank of China.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bloomberg News at 
 jliu42@bloomberg.net  